com.facebook.buck.android

Class NdkCxxPlatform

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.android.NdkCxxPlatform
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CxxPlatform

    public class NdkCxxPlatform
extends Object
implements CxxPlatform
    Interprets an Android NDK as a CxxPlatform, enabling our Android support to use our C/C++ support. The constructor for this class is parameterized by several configuration variables to determine which build and target platforms from the NDK to use.
